info.smart_tools.smartactors.core.cached_collection

Interface ICachedCollection

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CachedCollection

    public interface ICachedCollection
    Stores objects in memory by some key and may operate with these objects into DB Current collection contains documents with next fields: "": "keyValue" (value of should be defined as a parameter of collection) "startDateTime": "date and time of the beginning of activity of the document" "isActive" "true\false flag of activity of the document"
